OL,3,CSons pay tribute to biker parents
OL,4,Ckilled in multi-vehicle crash
OL,6,FA couple from Lichfield who died in a
OL,7,Fcrash on the A1 in Nottinghamshire are
OL,8,Fbeing remembered for their "unique
OL,9,Fenergies".
OL,11,FMike Savings, 66, and his wife
OL,12,FShirley, 64, were riding a Harley
OL,13,FDavidson trike motorcycle near
OL,14,FBassetlaw on Monday 20 July, when they
OL,15,Fwere involved in a collision with a
OL,16,Fcar and lorry.
OL,18,FEmergency services were called just
OL,19,Fafter 3.30pm but the couple were
OL,20,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
