PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784879327
OL,3,CSons pay tribute to biker parents
OL,4,Ckilled in multi-vehicle crash
OL,6,FThey had been riding around Scotland
OL,7,Fto celebrate their 41st wedding
OL,8,Fanniversary.
OL,10,FTheir sons have paid tribute saying:
OL,11,F"As those who were following their
OL,12,Fjourney will know, they had spent the
OL,13,Flast week on an anniversary tour of
OL,14,FScotland on their trike and were on
OL,15,Fthe final leg of their trip on the A1
OL,16,Fin Nottinghamshire when they were
OL,17,Finvolved in a road traffic incident of
OL,18,Fwhich they did not survive.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784879327
OL,3,CSons pay tribute to biker parents
OL,4,Ckilled in multi-vehicle crash
OL,6,F"They first met at a nightclub and
OL,7,Fafter over 40 years of marriage and
OL,8,Ftwo children their love of life and
OL,9,Feach other was still strong. Their
OL,10,Funique energies and perspectives will
OL,11,Fbe cherished and missed greatly by all
OL,12,Fwho knew them."
OL,14,FThe couple had visited a number of
OL,15,Flocations in Scotland including the
OL,16,FCommando Memorial at Spean Bridge to
OL,17,Fpay respects to Mr Savings' late
OL,18,Ffather who fought at D-Day.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
